{"tid":1082321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［毓民式獨］陳浩天：呼籲不要將香港問題直接投射到台灣，國民黨不會接受一國兩制。","createTime":"2019-03-29T01:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T18:35:42.000Z","uid":219007,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7ee3330a41efba1a5579f50136f9667f6a8d49","tid":1082321,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:20:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fuc0ujpJLO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFuc0ujpJLO8&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=e7304d62\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fuc0ujpJLO8</a><br />\n<br />\n岩先訓醒再聽多次再聽到陳浩天呢句判斷真係真心痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個從大中華夢醒覺既年輕竟然覺得國民黨唔會投共，真心想知黃毓民俾左咩迷藥佢食食到咁撚樣？<br />\n<br />\n仲叫人唔好將香港個套投射落台灣？<br />\n<br />\n呢D係乜野港獨派？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國民黨認同九二共識就已經接受一國兩制啦，天哥訓醒未？</span></span>"},{"pid":"c49c7110ccccbaea537bbf6c1229efcb339a66f3","tid":1082321,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"連登獨派點算？仲捧唔捧親愛嘅堡主好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b4c573cdff7b4ba8a7a9b7746afb2c0a7f0aee","tid":1082321,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c49c7110ccccbaea537bbf6c1229efcb339a66f3","tid":1082321,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"連登獨派點算？仲捧唔捧親愛嘅堡主好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"連登獨派多唔多人捧佢唔知<br />\n<br />\n但肯定既係天哥開始有倒退先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兆"},{"pid":"923a398e388b93d45d2e48d994b89dfa03cd8b28","tid":1082321,"uid":1372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7b4c573cdff7b4ba8a7a9b7746afb2c0a7f0aee","tid":1082321,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c49c7110